TITLE: Sequence Diagram for Multi-Tenant Request Routing in Cloud Agent
DESCRIPTION: This diagram illustrates the flow of tenant registration, authorization, and DIDCOMM message handling in a multi-tenant environment. It shows how a Cloud Agent manages tenant registration, wallet creation, and DID-to-tenant mapping in the database to ensure proper message routing.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hyperledger-identus/docs/blob/main/documentation/adrs/decisions/2023-05-09-message-routing-for-multi-tenant.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

